#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/cloak_of_arachnida.md:6
msgid "# Cloak of Arachnida _Wondrous item, very rare (requires attunement)_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/cloak_of_arachnida.md:8
msgid ""
"This fine garment is made of black silk interwoven with faint silvery "
"threads. While wearing it, you gain the following benefits:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/cloak_of_arachnida.md:13
msgid "You have resistance to poison damage."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/cloak_of_arachnida.md:13
msgid "You have a climbing speed equal to your walking speed."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/cloak_of_arachnida.md:13
msgid ""
"You can move up, down, and across vertical surfaces and upside down along "
"ceilings, while leaving your hands free."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/cloak_of_arachnida.md:13
msgid ""
"You can't be caught in webs of any sort and can move through webs as if they "
"were difficult terrain."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/cloak_of_arachnida.md:13
msgid ""
"You can use an action to cast the **_web_** spell (save DC 13). The web "
"created by the spell fills twice its normal area. Once used, this property "
"of the cloak can't be used again until the next dawn."
msgstr ""
